KYC Disclaimer

Introduction
The purpose of this KYC (Know Your Customer) process is to ensure the safety and security of all users participating in our platform. 
It is designed to prevent fraud, money laundering, and other illicit activities. 

By participating in our KYC process, you agree to provide accurate and truthful information.

DisclaimerDue Diligence: While we strive to create a secure and transparent environment, we cannot guarantee the complete accuracy or security of all data. 
Users are responsible for conducting their own research (DYOR) and due diligence before making any investment or participation decisions.

No Financial Advice: Our platform and any information provided through our channels do not constitute financial advice. 
We recommend consulting with a qualified financial advisor before making any investment decisions.

Risk Awareness: Cryptocurrency investments carry inherent risks, including the potential loss of your entire investment. Prices can be volatile and affected by various factors, including market demand, regulatory changes, and technological developments.

Compliance with Laws: Users are responsible for ensuring their compliance with all applicable laws and regulations in their respective jurisdictions. 
Participation in our platform is at your own risk, and we are not liable for any legal consequences that may arise.

Third-Party Information: We may provide links or references to third-party websites and resources. We do not endorse or guarantee the accuracy or reliability of any third-party content. 
Users are encouraged to verify information independently.

Data Privacy: Personal information collected during the KYC process will be handled in accordance with our Privacy Policy. 
We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the confidentiality of your data.

Conclusion
By participating in our KYC process, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this disclaimer. 
You agree to conduct your own research and seek independent advice where necessary. 
Our platform aims to facilitate a safe and compliant environment, but ultimate responsibility for investment decisions rests with the user.

For any questions or concerns, please contact our support team at [admin@blocxchain.org].
